<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standards was enacted in accordance with Paragraph 2, Article 48 of the Senior High School Education Act and Paragraph 1, Article 10 of the Charges and Fees Act.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Fees to be charged for the review, approval and revision of senior secondary school textbooks are as follows:
1. General schools:
(1) Review and approval fee: NT$25,000 per textbook
(2) Revision fee: NT$15,000 per textbook
2. Technical, comprehensive and specialized schools:
(1) Review and approval fee: NT$15,000 per textbook
(2) Revision fee: NT$7,500 per textbook]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standards shall take effect on the day of promulgation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
